tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE health_data (
  user_id INT,
  date DATE,
  steps INT,
  calories_burned INT,
  sleep_hours INT
);

CREATE TABLE health_data (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    steps INT,
    heart_rate INT,
    calorie_burned INT
);

CREATE TABLE user_profile (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    height FLOAT,
    weight FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE sleep_data (
    user_id UUID,
    date DATE,
    hours_slept FLOAT,
    quality_rating INT,
    resting_heart_rate INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id, date)
);

CREATE TABLE health_data (
    user_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    heart_rate INT,
    steps_count INT,
    calories_burned INT
);

CREATE TABLE exercise_data (
    user_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    activity_type VARCHAR,
    duration_minutes INT,
    calories_burned INT
);

CREATE TABLE nutrition_data (
    user_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    meal_type VARCHAR,
    calories_consumed INT,
    macros JSON
);
